BriteVerify,is,an,email,data,verification,platform,that,connects,with,email,domains,to,perform,real,time,account,status,verification,of,email,addresses,The,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,the,system,backend,with,rd,party,applications,The,data,elements,available,for,verification,are,Name,Email,Postal,Address,Phone,IP,Address,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON